text.tspan: Christ a Savior dead would be,
Not the One Who lives forever,
Christ a Savior dead would be,
Not the One Who lives forever,
Where the members of the Christ?
There to Him would be no Body,
Which His fullness is in life.
Then the church would n’er have been,
Which is both to Christ His dear bride
And to God the one new man.
With the voiding of His purpose,
